看题目说回旋踢，莫非，是rot13类加密？
写个脚本（仅小写字符）测试一下：
```python
s1="synt{5pq1004q-86n5-46q8-o720-oro5on0417r1}"
s2:str=""
for i in range(1,26):
    s2=""
    for letter in s1:
        if ord(letter)>=97 and ord(letter)<=122 :
            v1=ord(letter)+i
            if v1>122:
                s2+=chr(97+v1-123)
            else:
                s2+=chr(v1)
        else:
            s2+=letter
    print(s2)
    i+=1
```
